<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting uVision</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #334155;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1836 0%, #1e40af 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .welcome-message {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }
        .welcome-title {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        }
        .welcome-text {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .message-summary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #1e40af;
        }
        .summary-title {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
        }
        .summary-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .summary-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .summary-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
            min-width: 100px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .summary-value {
            color: #1e293b;
            flex: 1;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #dbeafe;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #1e40af;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .next-steps ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        .next-steps li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .contact-info h4 {
            color: #1e293b;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .contact-info p {
            color: #64748b;
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #0a1836;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer h3 {
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: #60a5fa;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .timestamp {
            background-color: #1e40af;
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .check-icon {
            color: #10b981;
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>uVision</h1>
            <p>Your Vision, Our Expertise</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-message">
                <div class="check-icon">âœ“</div>
                <h2 class="welcome-title">Thank You, <%= fullName %>!</h2>
                <p class="welcome-text">
                    We've successfully received your message and our team will review it carefully. 
                    We appreciate you taking the time to reach out to us.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="message-summary">
                <h3 class="summary-title">Message Summary</h3>
                <div class="summary-row">
                    <span class="summary-label">Subject:</span>
                    <span class="summary-value"><strong><%= subject %></strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-row">
                    <span class="summary-label">Submitted:</span>
                    <span class="summary-value"><span class="timestamp"><%= submittedAt %></span></span>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-row">
                    <span class="summary-label">Contact:</span>
                    <span class="summary-value"><%= email %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Review:</strong> Our team will carefully review your message within 24 hours</li>
                    <li><strong>Response:</strong> We'll get back to you via email with a detailed response</li>
                    <li><strong>Follow-up:</strong> If needed, we may reach out for additional information</li>
                    <li><strong>Resolution:</strong> We're committed to providing you with the best possible assistance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-info">
                <h4>Need Immediate Assistance?</h4>
                <p>For urgent matters, you can also reach us at:</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@uvision.com</p>
                <p><strong>Business Hours:</strong> Monday - Friday, 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM EST</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <h3>uVision</h3>
            <p>Connecting you with professional services that bring your vision to life.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> uVision. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="#">Twitter</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
